                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8716" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0571</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2299 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字赋能：舜天股份转“危”为“机”的“引擎计划”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital Empowerment: Sainty Share&#39;s&quot;Engine Plan&quot; to Turn &quot;Crisis&quot; to &quot;Opportunity&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许惠，陈益民，殷婧钰，张贞，胡非凡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏舜天股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字赋能；引擎计划；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Digital Empowerment ; Engine Plan</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从当前所处的国际背景和发展环境来看，贸易保护主义抬头，逆全球化浪潮兴起，全球价值链、产业链、供应链正在加速重组。坚持制造强国战略、深入推进制造业转型已经成为经济高质量发展的重要内涵。本案例以舜天股份从设计研发这一纺织服装产业价值链的源头出发，积极探索AI设计、3D制衣、元宇宙展示等数字化设计应用，打造数字化设计资源平台，塑造业务发展新动能、新优势为背景，重点描述了其开发的数字赋能培训项目，如何采用数字场景再现与实战订单交流这样的行动学习法在在公司内部实现数字资源整合，搭建沟通平台，真正实现对业务的数字赋能。本案例旨在基于数字化转型战略，探讨数字赋能为企业在逆境中扩展培训新边界，促进服装贸易行业的知识沉淀和管理方式变革提供经验借鉴。同时，学生通过案例学习也将深刻理解数字赋能的本质，以及掌握基于战略导向的培训需求分析和培训方法选择等知识的实践应用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">From the perspective of the current international background and development environment, trade protectionism is on the rise, the wave of anti-globalization is emerging, and the global value chain, industrial chain and supply chain are accelerating restructuring. Adhering to the strategy of a strong manufacturing country and deeply promoting the transformation of the manufacturing industry has become an important connotation of high-quality economic development. This case is based on the background that Sunshine Stocks, starting from design and development, which is the source of the value chain of the textile and apparel industry, has actively explored digital design applications such as AI design, 3D garment making, and meta-universe display to create a digital design resource platform, shaping a new kinetic energy and a new advantage of business development, and focusing on describing how the digital empowerment training program developed by Sunshine has adopted action learning methods such as the digital scenario reenactment and the exchange of actual orders to realize the digital resource development within the company. It focuses on describing how it developed a digital empowerment training program that uses action learning methods such as digital scene reproduction and real-world order exchange to realize digital resource integration within the company, build a communication platform, and truly realize digital empowerment for the business. Based on the digital transformation strategy, this case aims to explore digital empowerment as a way for enterprises to expand the new boundaries of training in the face of adversity, and to promote the knowledge precipitation and management change in the apparel trade industry. At the same time, students through the case study will also deeply understand the essence of digital empowerment, as well as master the practical application of knowledge based on strategy-oriented training needs analysis and training method selection.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《战略人力资源管理》、《培训与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化与数字赋能的概念；战略性培训与开发；培训需求模型；培训方法；培训效果评估模型；培训激励方式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
